                    <app><note>Text after Kaibel, compared against Paci</note></app>
                    <app loc="1"><rdg>ΚΑΛΑΝΔΕΙΝ</rdg><note>Bergk, ap. Kaibel from the stone</note></app>
                    <app loc="2"><rdg>[Φ]ε[βρ]αρίων</rdg><note>Paci</note></app>
                    <app loc="3"><rdg>ΗΛ...Α</rdg><note>Bergk, ap. Kaibel, from the stone, for ἡμ[έρ]α</note></app>
                    <app loc="4"><rdg>ϹΥΝΛΡΙΟϹΜΑΛΙΚΟϹΙΗΜΕ</rdg><note>Bergk, ap. Kaibel from the stone; reading here is that proposed by Kirchhoff (Kaibel "vix vera sunt"), followed by Paci</note></app>
