            <div type="translation">
                <p><!--translation(s) - add @xml:lang for 'en' or 'it' to div--></p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The text is preserved only in a manuscript tradition, and readings, particularly of the final line, depend upon conjectural interpretation of the letters originally recorded by Schubart.</p>
            </div>
